# Power BI Sales Dashboard Project

📊 A simple but effective sales dashboard created in Power BI using mock e-commerce data. This was my first hands-on Power BI project to explore data storytelling and dashboarding.

---

## 🚀 Project Objective
The goal of this project was to:
- Analyze monthly sales performance
- Identify best-selling product categories
- Create interactive visuals with slicers and filters

---

## 🛠️ Tools Used
- Power BI (for visualizations)
- Excel (for data cleaning)
- DAX (for creating calculated measures)

---

## 📈 Key Visuals
- Bar chart: Sales by month
- Pie chart: Sales by category
- Card visuals: Revenue, orders
- Slicers: Filter by product type, region

---

## 🧠 What I Learned
- How to build and structure a dashboard from scratch
- Importance of choosing the right visuals
- Using DAX for basic measures (Total Revenue, Avg Sales)
- User experience in designing intuitive dashboards

